node.text: My band and I were messing around and decided to do a rock & roll cover of fly me to the Moon by Frank Sinatra. It was just for rehearsals and wasn’t meant to be recorded this way, so that’s why it sounds rough. But it’s a vibe. Enjoy.

node.title: Fly me to the moon rehearsal edition

node.text: Excited to share my movie debut alongside @kristenanniebell @kirbyhowellbaptiste @paulwhausergram and Vince Vaughn. Directed and written by @arongaudet @gitapullapilly #Queenpins

node.text: Felt so good to be back! Thank you for having me Philly! Hope you all had a beautiful Fourth of July! 🇺🇸❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Bebe Rexha on July 01, 2021 tagging @hairbyiggy, @lilly_keys, @juleswstylist_, @ellenvonunwerth, and @ellenvonunwerthvon. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: Working with @ellenvonunwerth was one of my biggest dreams growing up. I remember seeing her photos on the internet and being just wowed every time. Her work with Rihanna are some of the most gorgeous photos I’ve ever seen. Thank you so much Ellen for shooting me, inspiring me, and being absolutely incredible. I hope you love what we shot as much as I do 🎂💄🐰
